  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study objective is to explore the safety and tolerability of STX209 in subjects with
      Autism Spectrum Disorders and to obtain preliminary data on several measures of efficacy in
      treating irritability. We hypothesize that STX209 will be safe and well-tolerated.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
